    "synopsis": "The conclusion of the Macharian Crusade. In the last years of his conquest, Macharius comes to Loki, a heavily industrialised world held by his arch-nemesis, the traitor Richter — once a trusted advisor, now turned renegade. Richter's betrayal is a symptom of the rot setting into the crusade: dwindling morale, dissent, and exhaustion. Brought to the very edge of the known galaxy and thrust into a plague-ridden hell of trench warfare, Macharius faces his sternest test, while Sergeant Leo Lemuel watches the legend he served begin to crumble. A bleak, mud-and-disease war story about how even the greatest conquests end — in betrayal, attrition, and a slow, grinding fall.",
